data.name: Air Conditioner Cum Air Sterilizer for Combined Application of Heating and Cooling
data.description: This system works on the application of psychrometric processes. Pre-filter, Hepa filter, and carbon-activated filters purify the air by 0.3 microns particles. Further, UVC emitter is used to kill the microorganism by destroying nucleic acid and disrupting their DNA.

data.name: Functional Weeder - Eyantra 2021-22
data.description: Designed an alphabot that was capable of sowing the seeds and picking up the weeds using the Elixir Programming language and Phoenix framework. I designed and 3D Printed the robotic arm and push mechanism for picking up the weeds and sowing the seeds.

data.name: ISIEINDIA- Indian Kart Racing Competition
